name: "Surfing" Dreams take on
description:
We have three good breaks close to where I live.  In between two of the breaks are a couple section breaks known only locally as “Pipe” (where a 3 ft. diameter pipe extends into the ocean) and Stables” (where there are some stables.  Makes sense.) .  When a local says where they are going they say we’re surfing “Pipe”: not, “The Pipe.” But “Pipe”.  Same with “Stables”    It’s like saying we are going to surf “Trestles”  Not “The Trestles”
